Version 3.1.1 - 2018-09-10 :
	* Fix error on installation


Version 3.1.0 - 2018-09-10 :

	* Fix creation of ISO > 4GB
	* Fix some errors with udisks2 (mount/unmount/loop-delete)
	* Fix DEBUG environment variable
	* Remove --force option
	* Replace -w option by -vv
	* Improve options parsing with getopt
	* Improve dependencies checking
	* Add support for loop devices with more than one partition
	* Add --overwrite-img/--overwrite-dir/--overwrite-iso options
	

Version 3.0.3 - 2018-03-29 :

	* Fix bug with tmpdir
	* Fix redirection to /dev/null


Version 3.0.2 - 2015-02-28 :

	* Add man-pages (English and French)
	
	
Version 3.0.1 - 2014-04-10 :

	* Fix bug with unprintable characters
	

Version 3.0.0 - 2014-05-17 :

	* Full rewrite of script
	* Support for translations (using PO files)
	* Remove --media and --about options
	* Script shows more informations by default
	* Add option --quiet, and rename option --vverbose in --+verbose
	* Remove ugly function trackerror() for little functions check*()
	* Suppress function initialize()

Version 2.4.0 - 2014-05-13 :

	* Add possibility to generate ISO from directory
	

